  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Awesome, thank you.\r\n\r\nFor reference for anyone else who needs something like this, I had to update the conditional like so:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nif (Array.isArray(values.data) && values.data.length <= 1) {\r\n    hide()\r\n} else {\r\n    show()\r\n}\r\n```",
