  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Since InstantSearch.js 3, you can use the [`panel`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/panel/js/) widget like this:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst brandMenuSelect = instantsearch.widgets.panel({\r\n  hidden: ({ results }) => results.getFacetValues('brand').data.length <= 1,\r\n})(instantsearch.widgets.menuSelect);\r\n\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  brandMenuSelect({\r\n    container: '#brand-list',\r\n    attribute: 'brand',\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2019-03-14T16:24:36Z",
